OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1784740728
OL,3,C'Scooby Doo' moment police unmask off-
OL,4,Croad biker
OL,6,FPolice say an off-road biker was
OL,7,Funmasked "like the end of a Scooby Doo
OL,8,Fepisode" after trying to ride off from
OL,9,Fofficers.
OL,11,FKeighley Neighbourhood Policing Team
OL,12,F(NPT) said in a social media post that
OL,13,Fofficers were on patrol in the
OL,14,FBraithwaite area of the town when the
OL,15,Fbike was ridden "directly towards us".
OL,17,FThey said he tried to ride round a
OL,18,Fpolice car but was blocked "by a
OL,19,Fcombination of our opening car door,
OL,20,Falong with a set of temporary traffic
OL,21,Flights on the pavement".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,337,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1784740728
OL,3,C'Scooby Doo' moment police unmask off-
OL,4,Croad biker
OL,6,FHe then abandoned the bike and tried
OL,7,Fto run off.
OL,9,FThe NPT said: "It didn't take long
OL,10,Fbefore he found himself in handcuffs,
OL,11,Fand his balaclava being removed like
OL,12,Fthe end of a Scooby Doo episode."
OL,14,FThe rider was reported for driving
OL,15,Fwithout a licence and insurance. The
OL,16,Fbike was seized by police.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/2
